reviewText: This is a Malaysian bootleg. There is no official English release on DVD or Blu-ray yet. This series was released by Pony Canyon in Japan across 6 box sets (2 episodes each). It has not been released in the US, though Funimation has translated it for digital streaming services. If you buy this, you're buying a knockoff.
I enjoyed this Anime. Both artwork and story was good! This Anime is all about Candy.
